{"title":"美国儿童一日","authors":["冯玉芝"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国儿童一日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据美国保卫儿童基金会最近公布的材料，美国一天中有："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７２名未满月的婴儿夭折；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１１０名未满周岁婴儿死亡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"９名儿童被枪杀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５名少年自杀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２７５３名少女怀孕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１０９９名少女打胎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１２８７名少女产下私生子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"９８８名儿童受到虐待；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３２８８名儿童离家出走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４９３２２名儿童在感化院；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２２６９名婴儿非婚出生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２９８９名儿童成为父母离异的牺牲品。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（５月５日《青年参考》冯玉芝译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}